&lt;li&gt;Assign global Harmonized Tariff Schedule (HTS) Classifications for Peloton’s new SKUs and product lines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in the execution of Peloton’s duty drawback and value reconciliation programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain timely and complete Customs recordkeeping for Peloton’s global imports and exports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct Denied Party Screening (DPS) in Peloton’s Global Trade Management (GTM) tool&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in the creation and continuous improvement of Peloton’s global trade compliance SOPs and policies&lt;/li&gt;
