&lt;h2&gt;Role Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotv4z65z9vgz72zz65z8r7z122zz81zz82zw2wz83zaz73zewsqa4z79zwz83zw9&quot;&gt;The Payments Team is responsible for building and maintaining Dropbox’s internal payments infrastructure — a robust, in-house alternative to third-party providers. The team supports all critical components of our financial ecosystem, including payment processing, authentication&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotv4z65z9vgz72zz65z8r7z122zz81zz82zw2wz83zaz73zewsqa4z79zwz83zw9 h-lparen&quot;&gt;(e.g.,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotv4z65z9vgz72zz65z8r7z122zz81zz82zw2wz83zaz73zewsqa4z79zwz83zw9&quot;&gt; 3DS), transaction flows, risk management, and revenue recognition.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qotv4z65z9vgz72zz65z8r7z122zz81zz82zw2wz83zaz73zewsqa4z79zwz83zw9&quot;&gt;As part of a strategic initiative to expand our global presence and to accelerate opportunities in Payments-driven revenue we’re building an entirely new Payments team based in Poland. The entire team, including engineering manager, product manager, and data scientist will be based on Poland. As a member of this new team, you’ll have the unique opportunity to shape the technical direction, culture, and processes of a high-impact engineering group from the ground up.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95lz89zy6z71zz79zz84zz68zyz69zupz72zz79zcz69zz76zkz79zp1z66ztz67zxz71zz89zz86zz71z&quot;&gt;Our Engineering Career Framework is &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;attrlink url author-d-iz88z86z86za0dz67zz78zz78zz74zz68zjz80zz71z9iz90z95lz89zy6z71zz79zz84zz68zyz69zupz72zz79zcz69zz76zkz79zp1z66ztz67zxz71zz89zz86zz71z&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;attrlink&quot; href=&quot;https://dropbox.github.io

&lt;h2 class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Role Description&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a Benefits &lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovw8w7fz78zz76zz85z3z83zz85zqz85zpz74ziz66zaz82zsz73zz80z0z85zz81zz79zrpp4z69z&quot;&gt;Partner&lt;/span&gt; to join our Global Benefits team! The &lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovw8w7fz78zz76zz85z3z83zz85zqz85zpz74ziz66zaz82zsz73zz80z0z85zz81zz79zrpp4z69z&quot;&gt;Benefits Partner &lt;/span&gt;will work as part of a small but mighty team to ensure Dropbox offers competitive benefits to Dropboxers, which are optimized for Dropbox’s business goals, values and culture.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovw8w7fz78zz76zz85z3z83zz85zqz85zpz74ziz66zaz82zsz73zz80z0z85zz81zz79zrpp4z69z&quot;&gt;This role combines program management, analytics, and stakeholder partnership, with the opportunity to help shape benefits offerings that support Dropboxers globally. You’ll gain exposure to global benefits strategy while collaborating with teams across People, Finance, Payroll, and HR Systems.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re passionate about benefits, self-motivated teammate with a curious nature, who loves partnering with colleagues to create delightful programs for employees, then this is the role for you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9uz65z1iz85zgdz68zmqkz84zo2qovw8w7fz78zz76zz85z3z83zz85zqz85zpz74ziz66zaz82zsz73zz80z0z85zz81zz79zrpp4z69z&quot;&gt;Support the management of international benefits programs across EMEA, APJ, and NAMER, including leave of absence, disability, life and risk insurance, medical, dental, vision, and pension plans.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot; author-d-1gg9

