&lt;h2&gt;Role Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Dropbox Growth team is seeking a Product Designer to create systems and experiences that measurably improve the lifecycle of our 700M+ global users.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll join a team dedicated to craft and the creative teams that rely on Dropbox every day. Your mission will be delivering impactful user experience improvements that elevate feature adoption, utilization, and retention for key functionalities most valued by our customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you’ll collaborate closely with Product Managers to transform business challenges and product hypotheses into tangible, quantifiable, and solvable customer problems. You’ll be empowered to design effective solutions and deliver elegant user experiences through close partnership with cross-functional peers. You’ll work hand-in-hand with Engineers to bring these solutions to life, ensuring a seamless and high-quality execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
