&lt;li&gt;Customer Focus. Understand customer needs and validate solutions through research and usability testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interaction &amp;amp; Visual Design. Design intuitive, efficient, and accessible experiences, applying strong interaction thinking and visual craft.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communication. Communicate clearly and proactively to ensure stakeholder alignment and informed decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solution Generation. Explore and iterate on solutions at varying levels of fidelity, informed by research, data, and best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Product Strategy &amp;amp; Decision-Making. Align design work to product strategy and business goals, engaging the right stakeholders to make timely decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Craft &amp;amp; Growth. Contribute to design critiques and continuously elevate quality

