&lt;h2&gt;Role Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Dropbox, we believe the future is built on great ideas. And great ideas don’t just come from the top; they come from everywhere. &amp;nbsp;Our mission is to design an enlightened way of working.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Engineering team is working to simplify the way people work together. They’re building a family of products that handle over a billion files a day for people around the world. With our broad mission and massive scale, there are countless opportunities to make an impact. This is just the beginning of how Dropbox will use AI/ML to enhance knowledge work in today’s work environment. We’re excited to bring a new generation of personalized AI-powered experiences in Dropbox to improve our customers&#39; working lives and a more focused, efficient, and productive workday.&lt;/p&gt;
